recognize today represent the best

00:04:30.290 --> 00:04:35.660
in children's literature, and
congratulations to all of you.

00:04:35.660 --> 00:04:39.060
You may also know that
Walter D. Myers was a friend

00:04:39.060 --> 00:04:41.140
