00:16:34.270 --> 00:16:36.230
I believe his work will
forever be celebrated

00:16:36.230 --> 00:16:40.450
for its profound civically
minded and communal impact.

00:16:40.450 --> 00:16:43.330
A body of work that shouted
across great distances

00:16:43.330 --> 00:16:45.920
to let people know
he cared about them,

00:16:45.920 --> 00:16:49.350
that they were not
alone, that they mattered.

00:16:49.350 --> 00:16:52.630
His work spoke to so many people
who felt unheard, dismissed,

00:16:52.630 --> 00:16:56.160
