margins of our society.

00:16:56.160 --> 00:16:57.640
Here's the problem.

00:16:57.640 --> 00:16:59.950
If the majority of
stories published, taught,

00:16:59.950 --> 00:17:03.830
and read are about people who
looked like me and experienced life

00:17:03.830 --> 00:17:06.610
like me, the underlying message is

00:17:06.610 --> 00:17:09.560
