00:17:54.740 --> 00:17:56.110
Black stories matter.

00:17:56.110 --> 00:17:57.520
Muslim stories matter.

00:17:57.520 --> 00:17:59.020
Immigrant stories matter.

00:17:59.020 --> 00:18:00.320
