our instincts as artists.

00:27:02.410 --> 00:27:05.470
To never allow our
imaginations to be walled off

00:27:05.470 --> 00:27:08.420
and to restore the
dignity, the compassion,

00:27:08.420 --> 00:27:13.420
the three dimensionality
of a boy such as Naeem.

00:27:13.420 --> 00:27:16.700
