if they were aware that this moment
was coming, if they could see us.

00:34:29.540 --> 00:34:32.830
Thomas Jefferson the man whose
books constituted the first attempt

00:34:32.830 --> 00:34:36.790
to rebuild this library after the
World of 1812, believed that people

00:34:36.790 --> 00:34:38.780
like me deserved to be mutilated.

00:34:38.780 --> 00:34:41.250
This isn't even an
indictment of the man.

00:34:41.250 --> 00:34:43.930
He owned human beings, and I
won't ever let anyone forget it,

00:34:43.930 --> 00:34:46.750
but on the issue of sodomites
he was miles more progressive

00:34:46.750 --> 00:34:48.240
than his peers.

00:34:48.240 --> 00:34:51.410
The rest of the men who built
this city probably would have just

00:34:51.410 --> 00:34:53.980
shrugged and had me put to death.

00:34:53.980 --> 00:34:57.510 position:56%
This is to say well I might not have
known all the historical details,

00:34:57.510 --> 00:35:02.260
I grew up with a keen understanding
that America was not for me.

00:35:02.260 --> 00:35:04.740
That the American dream
was a lie cooked

00:35:04.740 --> 00:35:08.810
up to keep normal people asleep
and people like me hungry.

00:35:08.810 --> 00:35:12.130
Sure the time had passed when
I could easily legally killed

00:35:12.130 --> 00:35:15.700
for putting on a dress, but the
legal niceties and the realities

00:35:15.700 --> 00:35:19.830
which trickle down to my frightened
young mind were vastly different.

00:35:19.830 --> 00:35:23.510
Television, books, movies,
religion, most adults,

00:35:23.510 --> 00:35:24.820
they all told me the same thing.

00:35:24.820 --> 00:35:28.300
Over and over sometimes without
knowing they were saying it.

00:35:28.300 --> 00:35:30.590
The American dream is not for you.

00:35:30.590 --> 00:35:32.650
The republic is not for you.

00:35:32.650 --> 00:35:35.400
Life among us is not for you.

00:35:35.400 --> 00:35:38.290
Even if you find people who love
you, your love will drag them

00:35:38.290 --> 00:35:40.030
down until you are killed

00:35:40.030 --> 00:35:43.580
and you will be killed,
and we will be happy.

00:35:43.580 --> 00:35:46.930
And yet, here I am in this city
built by men who have hated me --

00:35:46.930 --> 00:35:51.500
who would have hated most of us.

00:35:51.500 --> 00:35:55.390
Being honored for a career I
never believed I could have.

00:35:55.390 --> 00:35:58.150
