two of the flaws in their legacy,

00:36:17.750 --> 00:36:20.060
but probably not and who cares.

00:36:20.060 --> 00:36:24.190
The secret of the American dream
is that America itself is a dream.

00:36:24.190 --> 00:36:26.720
That America is as much the
faint hope of the slaved,

00:36:26.720 --> 00:36:30.530
